{"tid":1886352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國男童軍正式申請破產  因為太多性侵訴訟","createTime":"2020-02-19T00:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T09:50:17.000Z","uid":235174,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"dff12d0d75b4b451e1e0fce6de08b4b62f9d78af","tid":1886352,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:17:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200219/GYRDEA3XWLBAX3BZ2GT7NXLZEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200219%2FGYRDEA3XWLBAX3BZ2GT7NXLZEM%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=4b5fffed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200219%2FGYRDEA3XWLBAX3BZ2GT7NXLZEM%2F&h=f060c2e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200219/GYRDEA3XWLBAX3BZ2GT7NXLZEM/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2020/02/18/us/boy-scouts-bankruptcy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2Fus%2Fboy-scouts-bankruptcy&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=ff3f3035\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2Fus%2Fboy-scouts-bankruptcy&h=d0bb9593\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2020/02/18/us/boy-scouts-bankruptcy</a><br />\n陷性侵訴訟 美國男童軍總會申破產<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.snopes.com/tachyon/2017/10/AP_Boy_Scouts_FB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.snopes.com%2Ftachyon%2F2017%2F10%2FAP_Boy_Scouts_FB.jpg&h=eea5ed0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對數百宗性侵索償訴訟的美國男童軍總會，昨日向特拉華州聯邦法院申請破產保護，以成立賠償信託基金，賠償遭受性侵犯的成員。<br />\n<br />\n破產文件列出，總會資產介乎10億（78億港元）至100億美元（780億港元），負債五億（39億港元）至10億美元（78億港元）。案件進入破產程序可暫時擱置性侵訴訟，但最終可能被迫變賣財產，包括營地和遠足小徑，以籌集資金獲得逾10億美元的賠償基金。代表數百名聲稱被童軍性虐的律師莫內斯指，總會申請破產保護是童軍成年領導人隱瞞性虐行為數十年的結果。案件將總會所有訴訟移交一個法院，並試圖談判達成和解，而非動用總會資金為每宗訴訟打官司，但部份受害人可能得不到賠償。<br />\n財政緊絀人數大減<br />\n<br />\n在1910年成立的美國男童軍總會近年財政緊絀，童軍人數由上世紀70年代高峯時的逾400萬，大減至現時不足200萬。紐約州、阿利桑那州、新澤西州和加州通過立法，年代久遠性侵案的受害人更易入稟索償；總會最大收入來源的摩門教會，今年開始亦不再提供贊助。<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141cb69caee47a97aca5c53b8a08919c65f8b180","tid":1886352,"uid":170229,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:19:56.000Z","msg":"唯有轉行做牧師<br />\n教會大把錢"},{"pid":"91e430b229c6fa64c879ab0b312470f22980562d","tid":1886352,"uid":103230,"like":21,"dislike":12,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:24:02.000Z","msg":"on9先入童軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身呢個概念已經係離譜"},{"pid":"16f7a09f6b9ad30fc2fd85fd2ecf2b032863784d","tid":1886352,"uid":27319,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:28:07.000Z","msg":"童子軍跳彈床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a85d956bf583257a3a32dee63380fc05e6806a","tid":1886352,"uid":235174,"like":25,"dislike":5,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"91e430b229c6fa64c879ab0b312470f22980562d","tid":1886352,"uid":103230,"like":21,"dislike":12,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:24:02.000Z","msg":"on9先入童軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身呢個概念已經係離譜"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:30:11.000Z","msg":"你咁講係因為係香港同埋我地唔係白人, 出面D白仔幾撚鍾意camping, 香港童軍呃錢<br />\n依家美國好多細個玩過童軍既人好唔捨得, 個個響度讚果時係最美好既童年回憶, 慘在童軍總會比D變態佬害到要執<br />\n本來童軍結構就唔統一好難管下面D人條J"},{"pid":"b4b64eff398f94eb4b8448b36d38abf47b90abb7","tid":1886352,"uid":306614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pi